			<h4><a id="comment_link_64250924" name="comment_link_64250924" href="//it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23230986&amp;cid=64250924" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64250924)" >I wil guess that the surface must be rigid</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64250924" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64250924); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
